"title": "4312: bronze",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4312",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A metal highly prized for its strength and durability. It had a variety of uses in biblical times and was employed extensively in both the tabernacle and temple.</p>\n<h2>Bronze as a material used by craftsmen</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:22\">GEN 4:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:1-Exod31:6\">EXO 31:1–31:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:30-Exod35:34\">EXO 35:30–35:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:13-1Kgs7:14\">1KI 7:13–7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:15-1Chr22:16\">1CH 22:15–22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:7\">2CH 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:12\">2CH 24:12</a></p>\n<h2>Characteristics of bronze</h2>\n<h3>It was renowned for its strength</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:12\">JER 15:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:18-Lev26:19\">LEV 26:18–26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:23\">DEU 28:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:12\">JOB 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:18\">JOB 37:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:18\">JOB 40:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:27\">JOB 41:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:4\">ISA 48:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:18\">JER 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:20\">JER 15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:19\">DAN 7:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:13\">MIC 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>It was noted for its brilliance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:5-Dan10:6\">DAN 10:5–10:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:3\">EZK 40:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:15\">REV 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:18\">REV 2:18</a></p>\n<h2>The monetary value of bronze</h2>\n<h3>It was an expensive metal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:12\">REV 18:11–18:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:8-1Chr18:10\">1CH 18:8–18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:26-Ezra8:27\">EZR 8:26–8:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:13\">EZK 27:13</a></p>\n<h3>It was less valuable than gold or silver</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:17\">ISA 60:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:25-1Kgs14:28\">1KI 14:25–14:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:9-2Chr12:11\">2CH 12:9–12:11</a></p>\n<h2>Offerings of bronze were made at various times</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:24\">EXO 35:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:1-Exod25:7\">EXO 25:1–25:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:4-Exod35:9\">EXO 35:4–35:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:29-Exod38:31\">EXO 38:29–38:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:9-1Chr18:11\">1CH 18:9–18:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:14\">1CH 22:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:6-1Chr29:7\">1CH 29:6–29:7</a></p>\n<h2>Bronze was used in the tabernacle</h2>\n<h3>For the altar and its utensils</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:5-2Chr1:6\">2CH 1:5–1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:1-Exod27:6\">EXO 27:1–27:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:1-Exod38:6\">EXO 38:1–38:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:16\">EXO 35:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:39\">EXO 39:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:13\">NUM 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:39-Num16:40\">NUM 16:39–16:40</a></p>\n<h3>For the laver</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:18\">EXO 30:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:16\">EXO 35:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:8\">EXO 38:8</a></p>\n<h3>For the tent and the framework of the tabernacle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:17-Exod27:19\">EXO 27:17–27:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:17-Exod38:20\">EXO 38:17–38:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:10-Exod26:11\">EXO 26:10–26:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:36-Exod26:37\">EXO 26:36–26:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:9-Exod27:11\">EXO 27:9–27:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:9-Exod38:11\">EXO 38:9–38:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:18\">EXO 36:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:37-Exod36:38\">EXO 36:37–36:38</a></p>\n<h2>Bronze was used extensively in the temple</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:18\">2CH 4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:23-1Kgs7:33\">1KI 7:23–7:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:38-1Kgs7:45\">1KI 7:38–7:45</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:9-2Chr4:16\">2CH 4:9–4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:64\">1KI 8:64</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:17\">2KI 16:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:13-2Kgs25:17\">2KI 25:13–25:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:17-Jer52:23\">JER 52:17–52:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:8\">1CH 18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:2\">1CH 29:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:1\">2CH 4:1</a></p>\n<h2>Other uses of bronze</h2>\n<h3>For armour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:5-1Sam17:6\">1SA 17:5–17:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:38\">1SA 17:38</a></p>\n<h3>For weapons</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:16\">2SA 21:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:6\">1SA 17:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:35\">2SA 22:35</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:34\">PSA 18:34</a></p>\n<h3>For shackles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:21\">JDG 16:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:7\">2KI 25:7</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:7\">JER 39:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:11\">JER 52:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:11\">2CH 33:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:6\">2CH 36:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:15\">DAN 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:23\">DAN 4:23</a></p>\n<h3>For gates</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:16\">PSA 107:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:25\">DEU 33:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:13\">1KI 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:3\">1CH 22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:2\">ISA 45:2</a></p>\n<h3>For the bronze snake</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:9\">NUM 21:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:4\">2KI 18:4</a></p>\n<h3>For idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:4\">DAN 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20\">REV 9:20</a></p>\n<h3>For mirrors</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:8\">EXO 38:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:18\">JOB 37:18</a></p>\n<h3>For cooking utensils</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:28\">LEV 6:28</a></strong></p>\n<h3>For tools</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:22\">GEN 4:22</a></strong></p>\n<h3>For musical instruments</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:19\">1CH 15:19</a></strong></p>\n<h3>For statues</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:32\">DAN 2:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:35\">DAN 2:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:45\">DAN 2:45</a></p>\n<h2>Bronze as booty in war</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:7-Josh22:8\">JOS 22:7–22:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:21-Num31:23\">NUM 31:21–31:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:24\">JOS 6:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:8\">2SA 8:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:8\">1CH 18:8</a></p>\n<h2>The metaphorical use of bronze</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:39\">DAN 2:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:19\">LEV 26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:23\">DEU 28:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:18\">JOB 40:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:18\">JER 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:18\">JER 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech6:1\">ZEC 6:1</a></p>",
